Zm_metalcore_b1

Metal Core is  made that well, made with mostly metal structures and a lot of places to hide! This map is quite big and has a lot of room to run around and sneak around. 

There are some really cool "Easter Eggs" or so called 'hints' you can find. And one of the hints will lead you into a Disco Room! 

Remember, this is just a Beta! I wanted to make sure this map gets some words  in from other people so I could make it better!

thanks!


BoogerJay (Bjay)
